    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes "version 3" of the Layer Two Tunneling Protocol (L2TPv3).  L2TPv3 defines the base control protocol and encapsulation for tunneling multiple Layer 2 connections between two IP nodes.  Additional documents detail the specifics for each data link type being emulated. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
